sequenceDiagram
    participant Ops as Operator
    participant API as API Gateway
    participant RP as Replay Service
    participant PG as PostgreSQL
    participant K as Kafka

    Ops->>API: POST /api/v1/replay
    Note over Ops,API: dlqOnly, time range, or partition

    API->>RP: Replay request
    RP->>PG: List DLQ / events
    PG-->>RP: Unreplayed messages

    loop Each message
        RP->>K: Republish to target topic
        RP->>PG: Mark replayed_at
    end

    RP-->>API: replayed count
    API-->>Ops: 200 OK
